Key Match Events: South Africa scored 188 runs for the loss of 6 wickets in 20 overs. Aiden Markram scored 51 runs and Heinrich Klaasen scored 50 runs. Mohammad Nawaz took 2 wickets for 21 runs and Hasan Ali took 2 wickets for 28 runs.
Others: The match was played at The Wanderers Stadium, Johannesburg, South Africa. Adrian Holdstock and Allahudien Paleker were the field umpires. South Africa won the toss and decided to bat. Pakistan won the match by 4 wickets.
